msgid ""
"For letter finder,\n"
"\n"
"Son of Khoreg, son of Malgog, son of Agarabug, scribe of great clan of metal "
"land. Write about this time when we are very long in place and sun is pale "
"in sky and warm dies. No food grows but meat sometimes and mushroom in cave.\n"
"\n"
"Priest make offering to great warm and bang on pipe to stop clockwork demon "
"attack. Is hard now to teach to write and read. Food is want. Not book. Warm "
"is want. Burn book for warm.\n"
"\n"
"Is writing last word of clan of metal land. We probably eat each other "
"before warm again. Priest make offering. Chief look for place make warm. Old "
"map show way. Chief not read.\n"
"\n"
"Is not eat clanflesh. Is die. Is last to know read and write. Is eat by "
"others. Others live."
